lead_paragraph: Chris Coghlan hit a three-run home run, Stephen Vogt had three hits and the Oakland Athletics won their sixth straight, beating the Toronto Blue Jays 8-5 Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Athletics Beat Blue Jays 8-5 for Sixth Straight Win
